 app.project.item(index).numLayers 

Description <L=c#W></L><I=W>
The number of layers in the composition.

Type <L=c#X></L><I=X>
Integer; read-only.

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

CompItem.preserveNestedFrameRate <L=c#Y></L><I=Y>
 app.project.item(index).preserveNestedFrameRate 

