Type <L=c#1l></L><I=1l>
Integer, in the range  [0..720]  ; read/write.

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

CompItem.shutterPhase <L=c#1m></L><I=1m>
 app.project.item(index).shutterPhase 

Description <L=c#1n></L><I=1n>
The shutter phase setting for the composition. This corresponds to the Shutter Phase setting in the
Advanced tab of the Composition Settings dialog box.

Type <L=c#1o></L><I=1o>
Integer, in the range  [-360..360]  ; read/write.

