AVLayer.audioActive <L=h#9></L><I=9>
 app.project.item(index).layer(index).audioActive 

Description <L=h#a></L><I=a>
 true  if the layer's audio is active at the current time. For this value to be true,  audioEnabled  must
be true, no other layer with audio may be soloing unless this layer is soloed too, and the time must be
between the  inPoint  and  outPoint  of this layer.

Type <L=h#b></L><I=b>
Boolean; read-only.

