Duplicates the layer. Creates a new Layer object in which all values are the same as in this one. This
has the same effect as selecting a layer in the user interface and choosing Edit > Duplicate, except the
selection in the user interface does not change when you call this method.

Parameters <L=k#1n></L><I=1n>
None.

Returns <L=k#1o></L><I=1o>
Layer object.

