|  inType                          |  KeyframeInterpolationType       | The incoming interpolation type. |
|                                  | enum.                            | One of:                          |
|                                  |                                  |                                  |
|                                  |                                  | -    K                           |
|                                  |                                  | eyframeInterpolationType.LINEAR  |
|                                  |                                  | -    K                           |
|                                  |                                  | eyframeInterpolationType.BEZIER  |
|                                  |                                  | -                                |
|                                  |                                  |  KeyframeInterpolationType.HOLD  |
+----------------------------------+----------------------------------+----------------------------------+
|  outType                         |  KeyframeInterpolationType       | Optional. The outgoing           |
|                                  | enum.                            | interpolation type. If not       |
|                                  |                                  | supplied, the 'out' type is set  |
|                                  |                                  | to the  inType  value. One of:   |
|                                  |                                  |                                  |
|                                  |                                  | -    K                           |
|                                  |                                  | eyframeInterpolationType.LINEAR  |
|                                  |                                  | -    K                           |
|                                  |                                  | eyframeInterpolationType.BEZIER  |
|                                  |                                  | -                                |
|                                  |                                  |  KeyframeInterpolationType.HOLD  |
+----------------------------------+----------------------------------+----------------------------------+

