affects this keyframe only if the keyframe interpolation type is  KeyframeInterpolationType.BEZIER  for
both  keyInInterpolationType(keyIndex)  and  keyOutInterpolationType(keyIndex)  .

Parameters <L=K#3A></L><I=3A>
