Description <L=K#3D></L><I=3D>
Sets the incoming and outgoing temporal ease for the specified keyframe. See KeyframeEase object .

Parameters <L=K#3E></L><I=3E>
+----------------------------------+----------------------------------+----------------------------------+
| Parameter                        | Type                             | Description                      |
+==================================+==================================+==================================+
