|                                  |                                  | <L=K#1o>addKey</L> or            |
|                                  |                                  | <L=K#2L>nearestKeyIndex</L> .    |
+----------------------------------+----------------------------------+----------------------------------+
|  inTemporalEase                  | An array of 1, 2, or 3           | The incoming temporal ease.      |
|                                  | KeyframeEase objects             |                                  |
|                                  |                                  | -   If the property value type   |
|                                  |                                  |     is  PropertyValueType.TwoD   |
|                                  |                                  |     , the array contains 2       |
|                                  |                                  |     objects.                     |
|                                  |                                  | -   If the property value type   |
|                                  |                                  |     is                           |
