Property.setValueAtTime() <L=K#3O></L><I=3O>
 app.project.item(index).layer(index).propertySpec.setValueAtTime(time, newValue) 

Description <L=K#3P></L><I=3P>
Sets the value of a keyframe at the specified time. Creates a new keyframe for the named property, if one
does not currently exist for the specified time, and sets its value.

Parameters <L=K#3Q></L><I=3Q>
  Parameter    Type                   Description
  ------------ ---------------------- ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
   time        Floating-point value   The time, in seconds, at which to set the value. The beginning of the composition is 0.
