FootageSource.removePulldown <L=R#B></L><I=B>
 app.project.item(index).mainSource.removePulldown 
 app.project.item(index).proxySource.removePulldown 

Description <L=R#C></L><I=C>
How the pulldowns are to be removed when field separation is used. It is an error to set this attribute
if  isStill  is  true  . It is an error to attempt to set this to a value other than  PulldownPhase.OFF 
