| Parameter                        | Type                             | Description                      |
+==================================+==================================+==================================+
|  method                          |  PulldownMethod  enum.           | The method to use for            |
|                                  |                                  | estimation. One of:              |
|                                  |                                  |                                  |
|                                  |                                  | -                                |
|                                  |                                  |     PulldownMethod.PULLDOWN_3_2  |
|                                  |                                  | -    PulldownMethod.ADVANCE_24P  |
+----------------------------------+----------------------------------+----------------------------------+

Returns <L=R#M></L><I=M>
Nothing.

