TextDocument.hangingRoman <L=Z#1R></L><I=1R>
 textDocument.hangingRoman 

Note

This functionality was added in After Effects 24.0

Description <L=Z#1S></L><I=1S>
The Text layer's Roman Hanging Punctuation paragraph option. This is only meaningful to box Text
layers—it allows punctuation to fit outside the box rather than flow to the next line.

If this attribute has a mixed value, it will be read as  undefined  .

